ystems architecture (To Be models) with the Client\'s Architecture team and across the IT spectrum (Business, Applications and Infrastructure) with Board Level experience. Currently Yves works as the HP account CTO and Lead Enterprise Architect for the Belgium Public Sector. He runs a team of architects who are involved in various IT Roadmap and/or critical projects. He remains also active by delivering architecture for various domains. Besides that, he is working together with the Director Of Strategy And Innovation on providing innovation and strategy insight for all domains and agencies of the Flemish Government. '),(1742,468,'bio','Senior Lead Enterprise Architect '),(1743,468,'description',''),(1744,468,'time',''),(1745,468,'speaker',''),(1746,468,'_edit_last','2'),(1747,468,'_edit_lock','1389700960:2'),(1748,469,'_wp_attached_file','2014/01/yves-vanderbeken.jpg'),(1749,469,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:214;s:6:\"height\";i:308;s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"2014/01/yves-vanderbeken.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:26:\"yves-vanderbeken-50x50.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:50;s:6:\"height\";i:50;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"yves-vanderbeken-208x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:208;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(1750,469,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Yves Vanderbeken'),(1751,468,'_thumbnail_id','469'),(1752,468,'_wpas_done_all','1'),(1753,471,'biography',''),(1754,471,'bio',''),(1755,471,'description',''),(1756,471,'time',''),(1757,471,'speaker',''),(1758,472,'biography',''),(1759,472,'bio',''),(1760,472,'description',''),(1761,472,'time',''),(1762,472,'speaker',''),(1763,473,'biography','&nbsp