pan style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">To promote the</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> exciting innovation possibilities made available through </span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Open Data, </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">DataDays</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> are launching three new </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hackathon</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> competitions! </span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The competitions are sponsored and supported by, CORVE, V-ICT-OR, iDROPS and OKFN Belgium.</span></span></span><span><!-- Maybe be better to show the sponsors for each individual competition? --></span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span>Open Belgium Competition’s</span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\">Are you a programmer or designer? A hacker through and through? </span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">If so you can </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><i>be the first </i></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">to start working on what may well be Flanders most valuable data set - the VKBO, ‘the Enhanced Crossroads Bank for Enterprises’ - in which all enterprises, schools, hospitals etc. are geographically localised. Using the VKBO and Uit datasets in Vlaanderen, you can develop an application, produce mashups or create visualisations and present them to the public.</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">1. Professional Hackathon</span></span></span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Would you like to start your own company or launch a commercial application? If so, take part in the ‘Professional </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hackathon:’ </span></span></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Produce a working application </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Draft a business plan to present the results to citizens and entrepreneurs </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"