 Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">\r\nOver 30 ideas offering solutions to specific poverty related issues were conceived during eight creative miniLABs across Flanders. </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hack For Good</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> wants to turn these ideas into reality. We are asking digital developers, business developers, coders, programmers and hackers to pitch a plan to a panel of financiers on how to implement the ideas that they think are best. </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The best project will win</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> EUR 10,000 </span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">to boost social innovation. </span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\">Criteria for entry include: xxxxx</span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span>Open Europe</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span> | Open World Competition</span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">A</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><spa