r\n</i>\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"392\" title=\"VKBO\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>UiTdatabank</h3>\r\nDe UiTdatabank is, net zoals de VKBO, een databank die gegevens bevat over heel Vlaanderen. Indien u gebruik wil maken van deze gegevens kan u gemakkelijk aan de slag met een \"developer key\" die <a href=\"http://tools.uitdatabank.be/docs/out/sample-requests\" title=\"UiTdatabank Tools\" target=\"_blank\">u hier kan vinden</a>.','Data','','inherit','closed','open','','389-revision-v1','','','2013-12-20 18:06:40','2013-12-20 18:06:40','',389,'http://www.datadays.eu/389-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(395,3,'2014-01-06 10:30:04','2014-01-06 10:30:04','','Open Tools for Open Data: How data journalism affects the newsroom','','inherit','closed','open','','208-autosave-v1','','','2014-01-06 10:30:04','2014-01-06 10:30:04','',208,'http://www.datadays.eu/208-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(397,3,'2013-12-23 10:46:09','2013-12-23 10:46:09','','Mr. Tanguy De Lestré','','publish','closed','closed','','tanguydelestre','','','2013-12-26 16:03:15','2013-12-26 16:03:15','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=397',0,'dd-speaker','',0),(398,3,'2013-12-23 10:44:23','2013-12-23 10:44:23','','Tanguy De Lestré','','inherit','closed','open','','61e925793d82cf483a698e47ce7784f5','','','2013-12-23 10:44:23','2013-12-23 10:44:23','',397,'http://www.datadays.eu/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/61e925793d82cf483a698e47ce7784f5.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(400,3,'2013-12-23 13:14:44','2013-12-23 13:14:44','','Creative Commons and data projects. One license to rule them all','','inherit','closed','open','','267-autosave-v1','','','2013-12-23 13:14:44','2013-12-23 13:14:44','',267,'http://www.datadays.eu/267-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(401,3,'2013-12-23 13:21:49','2013-12-23 13:21:49','','Mr. Yannick H\'Madoun','','publish','closed','closed','','yannickhmadoun','','','2013-12-26 16:00:36','2013-12-26 16:00:36','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=401